                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8642" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2172</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1612 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色引擎，循环创效——ESG引领北元的绿色发展与经济效益双赢之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green engine, circular efficiency -ESG leads the way of green development and economic benefit in Beiyuan</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李瑞，谭思棋，刘耀南</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西北元化工集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北元集团；ESG战略；循环经济；绿色发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beiyuan Group; ESG strategy; Circular economy; Green development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在双碳目标的指引下，北元集团以ESG战略为引领，致力于实现经济效益与环保效益的双赢。集团通过绿色技术创新和节能减排措施，打造循环经济产业模式，以绿色生产为动力，促进北元集团的健康、稳定发展。同时，北元集团还注重社会公益与公司治理。北元集团积极参与社会公益活动，回馈社会，提升企业形象，加强公司治理，确保企业运营的合规性和透明度，不仅赢得了经济效益的“金”，更在绿色发展的道路上取得了显著成就，为化工行业的可持续发展树立了典范。本案例描述并分析了北元集团ESG战略实施的动因、措施与成效，旨在通过这一案例，引导学生全面理解ESG战略的内涵，包括环境、社会和公司治理三大维度的综合考量，以及如何通过这一战略框架实现企业的可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the guidance of the dual-carbon goal, Beiyuan Group takes the ESG strategy as the guidance, and is committed to achieving a win-win situation of economic benefits and environmental benefits. Through green technology innovation and energy conservation and emission reduction measures, the Group has created a circular economy industry model, and promoted the healthy and stable development of Beiyuan Group with green production as the driving force. At the same time, Beiyuan Group also pays attention to social welfare and corporate governance. The Group actively participates in social welfare activities, gives back to the community, enhances corporate image, strengthens corporate governance, and ensures compliance and transparency of corporate operations. It has not only won the &quot;gold&quot; of economic benefits, but also made remarkable achievements on the road of green development, setting a model for the sustainable development of the chemical industry. This case describes and analyzes the motivation, measures and effects of Beiyuan Group&#39;s ESG strategy implementation, aiming to guide students to fully understand the connotation of ESG strategy, including the comprehensive consideration of the three dimensions of environment, society and corporate governance, and how to achieve the sustainable development of enterprises through this strategic framework.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《企业社会责任》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；双碳战略；可持续发展理论；三重底线理论；企业社会责任；利益相关者理论；生态经济理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
